fig2A <- ggplotify::grid2grob(plot(clade_forest))
fig2B <- ggplotify::grid2grob(plot(cognate_forest))
fig2C <- ggplotify::grid2grob(plot(dysbiosis_forest)) 

figure2 <- plot_grid(fig2A,fig2B,fig2C,labels = c("A.","B.","C."),nrow=2,label_size = 16,rel_heights = c(1,1,1)) 
figure2

Save figure

ggsave("./figures/figure2.png",figure2,dpi=600,width=22.5,height=12.5,bg='white')
